> There is no error message. The program just silently exited when calling Ort::session.run().

As discussed, since we don't have any Windows ARM64 devices can you turn on verbose logging and see what was printed last? Also, it'll help if you can run it in a debugger and attach the output here.

Please see attached verbose output.

I don't think I can run with debugger since Visual Studio doesn't run on ARM64.

Thanks,

Hongyang
